dct_title_s: Floating LNG : evolution and development wallchart / Petroleum Economist Cartographic ; design, produced and distributed by Petroleum Economist with PETRONAS ; designed by K. Fuller and P. Bush. (Title panel)
dct_description_sm: Relief and depths shown by shading and gradient and bathymetric tints. Shows liquefied natural gas export plants and import terminals of the World. Accompanies: Petroleum economist, v. 83, no. 3, April 2016. "© Petroleum Economist, March 2016." Includes statistical tables, graphs, color illustrations and 1 inset map (South China Sea, Malaysia). Title panel and advertisement on verso. "Published March 2016".
dct_publisher_sm: London, United Kingdom : Petroleum Economist, March 2016.
